Package it.polimi.ingsw.Utils

Class ProxyDataInputStream

java.lang.Object
it.polimi.ingsw.Utils.ProxyDataInputStream
public class ProxyDataInputStream extends Object
The ProxyDataInputStream class is used to read UTF-encoded strings from a message dispatcher based on the message class.
